## Resuming After a Break

Start a fresh orchestrator session and say:

> Continue from where we left off.

The orchestrator reads CHANGELOG.md, IMPROVEMENTS.md, and recent reports to pick up context.

## Ending a Session

Say:

> Wrap up this session. Write a summary and update all tracking files.

