## Session Patterns

### Quick fix (15-30 min)
```
Start → "Fix [specific issue]" → Test → Review → Commit → Exit
```

### Feature work (1-2 hours)
```
Start → "Implement [feature]. Priorities: 1. X  2. Y  3. Z"
→ Delegate → Review check-ins → Test → Commit → Exit
```

### Exploration (30-60 min)
```
Start → "I want ideas, not changes. Analyse [area] and tell me what's possible."
→ Read proposals → Decide what to pursue → Exit
```

### Scrutiny (30-60 min)
```
Start → "Have the scrutinizer challenge [our approach / recent changes / architecture]."
→ Read findings → Discuss → Exit
```

### Self-directed improvement (1-2 hours)
```
Start → "Run 2-3 improvement cycles. Use your judgment. Produce comparison docs."
→ Review outputs → Redirect if needed → Exit
```

